{"tid":2497161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"案件開審控方仍未交齊文件予辯方 官直斥：咁樣公道咩？真係唔應該囉","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T10:38:13.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27aa21fc7a7b295eb1045be4c71317af9c22f305","tid":2497161,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:21:46.000Z","msg":"前年8⽉11⽇全港多處爆發反修例衝突，⾄12⽇凌晨有示威者在沙⽥警署外集結，警⽅清場拘捕多⼈。六男一女被控非法集結、襲警及無牌管有無線電通訊器等罪。案件原定今早在沙⽥裁判法院開審， 但主審裁判官因病缺席，主任裁判官溫紹明協助管理案件時，得悉控方今日仍有文件未交給辯方，連珠炮發批評控方：「你講真㗎？我以為我聽錯。好彩唔係我審。」「今日開（審）㗎啦喎原本，咁樣公道咩？真係唔應該囉。如果係你，你激唔激氣呀？」<br />\n<br />\n本案原訂審期12日，將縮減至9日。辯方同意，並透露其中<span class=\"red\">第四被告將會認罪</span>，而辯方亦不會就雷射筆專家提爭議。<br />\n<br />\n溫官翻查資料，問：「單案幾時訂審期㗎？半年前喎，<span class=\"red\">2020年10月7日排期，今日都未交齊</span>。阿Mr Hui，你嗰時都喺度㗎喎。」<br />\n<br />\n溫官並說，有時<span class=\"red\">控方向證人發問與案無關的問題</span>，變相令到裁判官「罰抄」，「你哋唔係由案發嘅時候問起喎，你哋由幾時加入學堂開始問起喎。我哋喺度抄抄抄，抄完先知唔關事，咁樣好痛苦㗎。浪費時間，浪費公帤，我哋啲人工都唔係平㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n案件早前提訊時，代表葉的⼤狀曾表示，葉看到有不知名被捕⼈⼠遭警員<span class=\"red\">「打到成頭都係⾎」</span>，然後該被捕者被帶到廁所後發出慘叫聲，有<span class=\"red\">便衣探員繼⽽問葉：「係咪想好似呢個⼈⼀樣？」</span>"},{"pid":"a7590d92cfcd6eeb61e3f42ffc6c7b4f618a7ea0","tid":2497161,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/VTQQTTX5PJEFDPSEPO76NLXWD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FVTQQTTX5PJEFDPSEPO76NLXWD4%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=e15038b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FVTQQTTX5PJEFDPSEPO76NLXWD4%2F&h=0306c695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/VTQQTTX5PJEFDPSEPO76NLXWD4/</a>"},{"pid":"34e34f6fd5f5fd089cb850aa02342b88f62d44b3","tid":2497161,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"溫官真係玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee42b16348e32864766581c84b1bbc97c7e6b1c","tid":2497161,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"負責審理本案的裁判官崔美霞身體抱恙，故交由署理主住裁判官溫紹明另訂審期，最終排期至下週一開審，屆時其中一名男工程師會改為認罪。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-12-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0-7-%E4%BA%BA%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E6%A1%88%E5%8E%9F%E4%BB%8A%E9%96%8B%E5%AF%A9-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E9%81%B2%E4%BA%A4%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%94%94%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2-%E5%85%AC%E9%81%93%E5%92%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-12-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0-7-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BB%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2581%25B2%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%2592%25A9%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=1981ec02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-12-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0-7-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BB%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2581%25B2%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%2592%25A9%2F&h=2382c18e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-12-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0-7-%E4%BA%BA%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E6%A1%88%E5%8E%9F%E4%BB%8A%E9%96%8B%E5%AF%A9-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E9%81%B2%E4%BA%A4%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%94%94%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2-%E5%85%AC%E9%81%93%E5%92%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"ac8bf66b1c55b3fd266f4b0061c09d96dbeb579d","tid":2497161,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd15957645aec58aa6cc7691d3f98bd814876b9d","tid":2497161,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"崔官好似請咗好耐假？"},{"pid":"9ac6ef1e177dfdf5520bac7bf7f2b42095b58cb6","tid":2497161,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd15957645aec58aa6cc7691d3f98bd814876b9d","tid":2497161,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"崔官好似請咗好耐假？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"2星期啫"}]}